        - ``"sample"`` → ``sample_id``
        - ``"feature"`` → ``feature_id``

        If not specified, defaults to the current index type.

        Args:
            id_type: One of ``"taxon"``, ``"assembly"``, ``"sample"``,
                ``"feature"``.

        Returns:
            Self for chaining.
        """
